movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Worth watching for the ending!!!
review: For those of you who hated Jar Jar Binks and wished for him to meet some gruesome end that would turn even Jabba The Hut's stomach, well, I seem to remember wishing exactly that on C3P0 when first seeing star wars. So if you kinda ignore Jar Jar, the movie is pretty darn good and I must say, the ending matched any Star Wars movie, which is more than I can say for 'Attack Of The Clones'.
